{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Cursed School</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a catastrophic thunderstorm, an ancient curse descends, transforming Sakuradoki High School into a living hell. The awakened survivors gradually lose their sanity, their souls are devoured by desire and fear, turning them into bloodthirsty and brutal monsters...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Parry, Slash and Survive!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Soul Devourer is a metroidvania action-platformer with a striking anime horror art style. Explore the cursed Sakuradoki High School, master powerful abilities, battle twisted monsters, and uncover the long-buried dark secrets hidden beneath the school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530620/extras/cover-art-6-xs.jpg?t=1730295909\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sekiro-inspired Parry System:\u00a0</strong>Actively parry enemy attacks, expose their weaknesses, and unleash a powerful counterattack!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530620/extras/parry-1.gif?t=1730295909\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Twisted Monsters:\u00a0</strong>Fight against over 70 twisted monsters, each with unique behaviors and attacks. And challenge over 10 ferocious bosses, exploit their weaknesses, defeat them and get unique abilities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530620/extras/fight-1.gif?t=1730295909\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Exploration:</strong> Explore over 10 unique main areas in a vast, interconnected game world full of excitement. Also collect souls scattered around the game world, that allow you enhance your character, master new abilities, customise your gameplay and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530620/extras/explore-1.gif?t=1730295909\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Long-buried Secrets:</strong>\u00a0Uncover the secrets buried deep beneath the school, encounter mysterious characters, collect a variety of clues, forge your path towards the truth of the ancient curse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530620/extras/secret-1.gif?t=1730295909\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730295909","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530620/page.bg.jpg?t=1730295909","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530620/5739545fe04e35c56e3d93033b04aecbcdcd370f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730295909","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530620/5739545fe04e35c56e3d93033b04aecbcdcd370f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730295909","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2531850,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Cursed School</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a catastrophic thunderstorm, an ancient curse descends, transforming Sakuradoki High School into a living hell. The awakened survivors gradually lose their sanity, their souls are devoured by desire and fear, turning them into bloodthirsty and brutal monsters...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Parry, Slash and Survive!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Soul Devourer is a metroidvania action-platformer with a stri